  "texts": [
    "I hate writing essays and struggle with them, but you still have to do them\" Eight students went into more explanation as to why they would be unsupportive: \"Generally unsupportive, as they would be loosing out on the experience of writing an essay and the learning gained from it.",
    "Although feel like university assessments need to adapt to take into account the existence of AI assistance. \"",
    "\"Unsupportive of it because I think its unfair to not come up with ideas on your own and have to rely on AI to convey your thoughts.",
    "Its important to be able to phrase and think clearly without external influences clouding or swaying your thought process. \"",
    "\"Unsupportive -the AI is limited by the data on which it is modelled."
  ]
}